Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

To use Einstein Discovery, you must Set Up Einstein Discovery, Get Started Using Einstein Discovery. Define Your Target Outcome and Prepare Data for Analysis.

You can Create a Model, Open a Model, Navigate a Model, Edit Model Settings, Track Model Versions, Handle Quality Alerts.

Handle Quality Alerts includes No Correlation Alert, Disparate Impact Alert, Proxy Variable Alert, Outliers Alert, Strongest Predictors Alert, Multicollinearity Alert, High Cardinality Alert, Missing Values Alert, Identical Values Alert, Recommended Buckets Alert, Dominant Values Alert, No Correlation Alert, Imbalanced Distribution Alert, Potential Data Leakage Alert.

Predict & Improve Outcomes and Decision Optimization (Beta) are also part of Einstein Discovery.
title: No Correlation Alert in Einstein Discovery
